<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Pas-paa-hvis-du-koeber-biopejse" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Pas-paa-hvis-du-koeber-biopejse" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Pas-paa-hvis-du-koeber-biopejse" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Pas på, hvis du køber biopejse&body=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Pas-paa-hvis-du-koeber-biopejse" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>En producent eller importør må kun bringe lovlige og sikre produkter i omsætning, og Sikkerhedsstyrelsen har udført markedskontrol på ethanol biopejse på baggrund af indberetninger om ulykker i forbindelse med produktet. Produkterne har ikke fejlet på afgørende sikkerhedsmæssige områder, men overvejer du at købe en biopejs, er der en række ting, du bør være opmærksom på, da der ikke findes ensartede regler for produktet i EU. Sikkerhedsstyrelsen har sat emnet på dagsordenen i EU, og fået opbakning til en arbejdsgruppe, der skal arbejde med et standardiseringsmandat vedr. sikkerhedskrav til biopejse.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/embed.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/embed.tpl) -->
<div class="embed-file ">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/embed/file.tpl (design:content/view/embed.tpl) -->
<div class="content-view-embed">
    <div class="content-body">
      <a class="mime pdf" href="../../../content/download/5561/77087/version/1/file/Report%2b-%2bBio%2bfireplaces%2b-%2bv5-3%2b(2).14a4">Læs fælleseuropæisk rapport om sikkerhedsforanstaltninger ved biopejse</a> (PDF)
   </div>
</div>
<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/embed/file.tpl (design:content/view/embed.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/embed.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/embed.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="../../../Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2009/Information-til-forbruger" title="Link til pressemeddelelse" target="_self">Læs også pressemeddelelse om information til forbrugere om biopejse</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Køb og brug af biopejse</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Som forbruger bør du være speciel opmærksom på følgende i forbindelse med køb og brug af en biopejs:</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Krav til underlagets beskaffenhed</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Uanset om din pejs skal hænge eller stå, bør det fremgå i brugervejledningen, hvilke krav der af hensyn til brandfaren stilles til underlaget.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Ventilation</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Det bør også tydeligt fremgå af vejledningen, hvor stort et rum skal være, før man må benytte pejsen. Afbrændingen af ethanol bruger ilt og udleder kultveilte Co2, og i et lille rum er der risiko for, at det omdannes til kulilte, hvilket er både giftigt og farligt. Derfor bør pejse ikke bruges i rum, man sover i eller i rum under jordhøjde, uanset rummets størrelse. Det bør også oplyses, om der er behov for ventilation i rummet ved brug af pejsen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Ophængning/montering af pejsen</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Det bør fremgå, hvordan den skal monteres eller hænges op. Der bør også stå, hvilke beslag, rawlplugs, skruer etc. der skal bruges. Når man overvejer placering, bør man tænke på, at børn og husdyr skal holdes på behørig afstand af de åbne flammer.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Afstand til brandbare materialer</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Producenten bør have taget stilling til sikkerhedsafstand til fx gardiner, møbler og lignende brændbare materialer. Det bør også fremgå, om man må stille ting på eller ved pejsen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Angivelse af brændstoftype</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Fabrikantens anbefaling til valg af brændstoftype bør fremgå og følges.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Påfyldning af ethanol, køletid og mængder</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Vejledningen bør indeholde information om, hvordan man fylder brændstof på pejsen. Den bør også indeholde oplysning om, hvor lang tid der skal gå, før det er sikkert at fylde på igen. Samtidig bør det fremgå, at man nøje skal kontrollere, om den reelt er gået ud før genopfyldningen, og hvordan man gør det.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Opbevaring af brændstof</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Alle beholdere med brændstof skal være med børnesikrede skruelåg. Brandfarlige væsker er omfattet af beredskabslovgivningen. </p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="http://brs.dk/omstyrelsen/presse/nyheder/Pages/2012_01_04.aspx" title="Link til beredskabslovgivningen" target="_self">Link til beredskabslovgivningen</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Optænding af pejsen</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Det bør fremgå af vejledningen, hvordan man tænder pejsen på en sikker måde, fx om det er en god ide at bruge en fyrfadslighter.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Slukning af pejsen</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Brugervejledningen bør indeholde anvisninger om, hvordan man slukker pejsen, også i forbindelse med et uheld. Brug aldrig vand, som ikke er i forstøvet form, da det kan resultere i brandspredning. </p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Vedligehold og rengøring</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Forbrugeren bør informeres om, hvordan pejsen skal holdes ren. </p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Gå aldrig fra en tændt pejs</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Det bør fremgå af vejledningen, at pejsen bør være under konstant opsyn af en voksen person, når den er tændt.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
